A Prime Location: Easy trail access to Lake Padden & close to Fairhaven, South Bellingham School District, Minutes to WWU campus. Spacious home in rarely available Tioga Mobile Home Park. 3 bedroom and 2 full bath home with plenty of room for entertaining or relaxing, snuggled up with a fire in the wood burning stove. Large windows let in plenty of natural light. Spacious kitchen is a chef's dream. Newer water heater. Lot space is large with fence, raised garden beds and established flower garden in front. Lot rent includes water and septic. Located close to either Bellingham or Ferndale. Easy access to I-5.

Experience coastal living at its finest with tranquil views of 10, 000 trees and glimpses of Chuckanut Bay. This custom home, set on a quiet & private lane, blends elegance and functionality. The upper-level primary suite boasts a luxury-hotel like bathroom and custom walk-in closet. The European-inspired kitchen features granite countertops and upscale Jenn-Air appliances. Expansive windows and custom French doors flood the main living area with light, opening to a spacious deck. The lower level offers flexible spaceideal for a home office, teen retreat, or multigenerational living. Minutes from Fairhaven, this home is perfect for work-from-home professionals or households with older kids seeking space and comfort.

This superior split-level home offers breathtaking territorial views and high-quality finishes throughout. Enjoy granite countertops, beautiful hardwood floors, and a spacious living room with high ceilings and large windows that frame the scenery. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The massive primary bedroom features a 5-piece bath and walk-in closet. Step outside to an extra-large deck, perfect for entertaining. The 2-car garage includes additional shop space and smart red light motion detection for easy parking. Native growth perennial landscaping adds natural beauty. A true gem!

Sunset Drive in popular Birch Bay Neighborhood. Triple wide home on 2 lots, creating a great value should you want to add a second home. Home is spacious with an amazing kitchen, with lots of storage, walk-in pantry, and eating bar. All bedrooms are large, especially the primary, which feature a walk-in closet and spacious bathroom. There is a gas fireplace in the living room and a covered deck off the living room, which has a view of the waters of Birch Bay. The detached garage fits 2 vehicles comfortably and has an area for a small workspace. Across the street is a walking path, which will take you to the beach in about 5 minutes. You are just minutes from the State Park and hub of busy Birch Bay featuring fine dining and entertainment.

This single-level home offers convenient living just a short walk from the extensive trail system, Bellingham Technical College (BTC), and Squalicum Beach, where an exciting new pier is set to enhance the waterfront. Recently refreshed with new paint and carpets, this property features a low-maintenance yard, making it perfect for those seeking ease of upkeep. The open floorplan boasts surprisingly spacious rooms for comfortable living and entertaining. An oversized 2-car garage accessed from the alley provides ample storage and additional parking off the alley. The living room has a freestanding gas stove, providing efficient and economical heating for the entire home. The house is also an excellent candidate for solar panel installation.
nearby_schools: Bellingham Public Schools, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Step into your brand-new dream home! This modern gem offers a bright, open-concept design with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a spacious one-car garage complete with over 200 sq. ft. of loft storage. Soaring vaulted ceilings, radiant concrete floors, and an abundance of natural light paired with sleek LED lighting create an inviting atmosphere. The primary suite features a generous walk-in closet and a luxurious spa-style shower. The kitchen shines with quartz countertops, contemporary white cabinetry, and its own dedicated water heater for added ease. Outside, enjoy a partially fenced backyard that backs onto serene green space. This home isnt just about the stunning detailsits also part of an incredible community!
